title: About the app
description:
Create a "About the App" module from the text module (they should be 2 unique modules instead of a text module that is configured)
The About the app module should be a default module in all apps
It should contain the QuickSeries branding
It should pull the data from the about API
It should update the content when ever a use is visiting that module, but it should load from storage to prevent a flash

title: A module with a really long name - should be displayed on at least three rows
